    Get parameter estimates and model estimates

    par_est.Rd

    Get parameter estimates and model estimates

    Usage

    par_est(mod)

    Arguments

    mod

    Fitted model object

    Value

    List with model estimates (pred_res) and parameter estimates (par_summary)

    Examples

    dat <- sim_slr(n_sim = 30)
mod <- run_mod(dat, model = "slr")
#> module glm loaded
